OL,6,FIn a statement, the transport
OL,7,Fsecretary said she discovered "some
OL,8,Ftime later" that the phone had not
OL,9,Fbeen taken and that she had made a
OL,10,F"genuine mistake", from which she "did
OL,11,Fnot make any gain".
OL,13,FShe added that magistrates gave her
OL,14,Fthe "lowest possible outcome".
OL,16,FMs Haigh, in her statement said: "In
OL,17,F2013 I was mugged while on a night
OL,18,Fout. I was a young woman and the
OL,19,Fexperience was terrifying.
