OL,6,F"The original work device being
OL,7,Fswitched on triggered police attention
OL,8,Fand I was asked to come in for
OL,9,Fquestioning. My solicitor advised me
OL,10,Fnot to comment during that interview
OL,11,Fand I regret following that advice.
OL,13,F"The police referred the matter to the
OL,14,FCPS and I appeared before Southwark
OL,15,Fmagistrates. Under the advice of my
OL,16,Fsolicitor I pleaded guilty ` despite
OL,17,Fthe fact this was a genuine mistake
OL,18,Ffrom which I did not make any gain.
