OL,6,FIt is understood that it was a fraud
OL,7,Foffence and the incident was disclosed
OL,8,Fin full to Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,9,FStarmer when she joined the shadow
OL,10,Fcabinet. The conviction is now spent.
OL,12,FThe chair of the Conservative Party
OL,13,Fsaid the prime minister has "serious
OL,14,Fquestions" to answer about the matter.
OL,16,FNigel Huddleston said in a statement:
OL,17,F"These are extremely concerning
OL,18,Frevelations about the person
OL,19,Fresponsible for managing #30 billion
OL,20,Fof taxpayers' money.
